name: cred-rea-fish-team-stationary-point-count-surveys-at-wake-pacific-remote-island-areas-pria-2005
notes: Stationary Point Counts at 4 stations at each survey site were surveyed as part of Rapid Ecological Assessments (REA) conducted at 14 sites around Wake in the Pacific Remote Island Areas (PRIAs) during 12 October - 30 October 2005 in the NOAA Oscar Elton Sette (OES0513) Reef Assessment and Monitoring Program (RAMP) Cruise. Raw survey data included species level abundance estimates.
